{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"c39ddf1b-ce80-4fc0-b763-b6b6e3a15baa","content":"There's no workflow file in the current directory. Since I can't review your specific workflow, here's a concise guide for switching to **NuGet trusted publishing (OIDC)**:\n\n### 1. Register your package on NuGet.org\n\n- Go to **nuget.org → Manage Packages → your package → Trusted Publishers**\n- Add a new **GitHub Actions** trusted publisher, specifying:\n  - Repository owner/name\n  - Workflow filename (e.g., `publish.yml`)\n  - Optionally: environment name, branch/tag filters\n\n### 2. Update your GitHub Actions workflow\n\n```yaml\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    # Required for OIDC token\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write\n      contents: read\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v4\n        with:\n          dotnet-version: '8.x'\n\n      - run: dotnet pack -c Release\n\n      # Use dotnet nuget push with --api-key is NO LONGER needed\n      - name: Push to NuGet\n        run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg\n          --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\n### Key changes\n\n| Before (API key) | After (OIDC) |\n|---|---|\n| `secrets.NUGET_API_KEY` in `--api-key` | No API key needed |\n| No special permissions | `permissions: id-token: write` |\n| N/A | Trusted publisher registered on nuget.org |\n\n### 3. Clean up\n\n- Remove the `NUGET_API_KEY` secret from your repo/org settings once verified.\n\nThe `dotnet` CLI (v8.0.4+) automatically detects the OIDC environment and requests a token from GitHub's OIDC provider when no `--api-key` is supplied and trusted publishing is configured on nuget.org.\n\n> **Note:** If you use an **environment** in your workflow (e.g., `environment: production`), make sure the same environment name is registered in the trusted publisher config on nuget.org.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"b66e7739-215a-40a1-9116-f45854980b38","outputTokens":519,"requestId":"C002:14268C:8083B0A:8EACEF0:69EABE8F"},"id":"41322b9d-2a2c-428b-be1f-d3e387226a6c","timestamp":"2026-04-24T00:51:40.348Z","parentId":"5fe12cf7-fccb-4c36-8122-ac49a8dd6b2f"}
